ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectRegulations Amending the Migratory Birds Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the Migratory Birds Regulations, in order to change some hunting season dates for the 2009-2010 hunting season and to set daily bag limits and possession limits for migratory game birds to ensure the sustainable harvest of migratory game bird populations.
